data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this stunning home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. You will admire the vaulted 2-story ceilings that lend an airy feel to the spacious living area. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, there's ample space for everyone to relax and unwind. The kitchen is a culinary delight with sleek granite countertops, matching stainless maytag appliances and ample storage space. The lower level boasts two bedrooms, a cozy family room, and a spacious utility room that can be easily divided to add a 5th bedroom, providing flexibility and convenience for your family's needs. Step outside onto your large deck to overlook your own private retreat—a fully fenced backyard with a charming patio, ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying a peaceful moment. The backyard shed allows for yard upkeep and gardening storage allowing you more space in the garage. Check out the supplements for a list of updates made throughout your new home!
